com.tractrac.model.lib.api.map

Interface IMapItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAttachable, IIdentifiable, IMetadataContainer, INamed, IPropertiesContainer, com.tractrac.util.lib.api.serialize.ISerializable

    public interface IMapItem
extends INamed, com.tractrac.util.lib.api.serialize.ISerializable, IMetadataContainer

    A tangible object that can be drawn in the viewer. They consist of one or more IPositionedItem, and this relationship is used to render them on a map. They can be also part of the route through the IControlRoute

    Each map item is composed by one or more physical IPositionedItems.
